author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at what appears to be Reddit's largest community surrounding Art, on the surface everything seems fine but like most communities it's moderated by the most power hungry people you'll find behind a keyboard who live to ruin the online experience of millions each and every day. Thanks for watching!

title: Reddit's Most Disgusting Moderators Just Quit...
